f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06cb919c0baf4b17f215ab967cce126769b76ac","tid":2197538,"uid":126382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7c16edc34f39913e35b37687eeef1e7c295c150","tid":2197538,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"啲封面立繪主題曲根本冇咩意思，點解要嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要放舊錢落介面同game sound好過"},{"pid":"1c1ea918136373dad7c36733911fcd45e565cb78","tid":2197538,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲封面立繪主題曲根本冇咩意思，點解要嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不<span class=\"red\">如</span>放舊錢落介面同game sound好過</blockquote>"},{"pid":"23a8670590d759002b1c607f2bb75c6e9d3aa15a","tid":2197538,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148576ede7185e66e04b64b0a0647fbb72d91ef2","tid":2197538,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"睇落好正"},{"pid":"4906bb72f54f5f053ccae6ee81974ea1cef337c0","tid":2197538,"uid":143402,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"講真樓主如果想成功可以試吓埋大陸堆，可以攞到好多資源同關注度，上面嘅玩家對於國產遊戲係撐到十足十，只要唔係做出嚟Hea鳩佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n如果一開波想淨係靠香港同海外係冇可能成功的。"},{"pid":"189dc096ca48f1763f81c8f1e18165b253f8de46","tid":2197538,"uid":159726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"再push下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b63500e51b19dea7f3acfc48c29aa4766baa79","tid":2197538,"uid":220226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"支持火柱～<br />\n港驚出左必買"},{"pid":"71c9f22e2f9d121bf367b1d52a585080ec8ae0a1","tid":2197538,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">好多人唔係想賺大錢，真係只係想創作。</span><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但香港好似唔容許你有自由意志咁<br />\n好多行業淨係自給自足都已經困難<br />\ne.g.記者<br />\n<br />\nbtw,已買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},{"pid":"187ad4f4cfeb67e1fc55acb4f519453c6d7129b0","tid":2197538,"uid":56582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n隻game真心唔錯嘅"},{"pid":"b9f6483cf04ffd409f6f6cb111038c542cfaf6ca","tid":2197538,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181d32e6b2070a03f82d8f9f940de0aa78b9ddc7","tid":2197538,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"推，支持<br />\n巴打有需要做翻譯/校對我可以幫手"},{"pid":"bc3a8c8554aef9301e1781c84192d03cb4940754","tid":2197538,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"c8893f6da32134b55eace8a2e2837af31a3788db","tid":2197538,"uid":78613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"見到abyss諗起來自深淵....<br />\n我愛黎明...."}]}